The '''Offen''' was a [[Species/Legends|species]] that was relatively new to the concept of space travel by the [[Time/Legends|time]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. They where led by a [[Unidentified Offen queen|Offen queen]] who was 6,000 [[Standard year|years]] old in [[17 ABY/Legends|17 ABY]].<ref name="TERC">''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]''</ref><ref name="SWE">''[[Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

